    "(2) We eliminated duplicate instances that have the same text and trigger word position.",
    "(3) We removed instances where the trigger word position surpasses the maximum sentence length (128).",
    "We conducted ablation experiments to validate the effectiveness of conditional adversarial learning on the GLUE benchmark [40].",
